{"tid":716538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專責小組建議保留高級文憑和副學士 但資歷須重新定位","createTime":"2018-06-25T10:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T12:26:30.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f108588d0f12b42d3b25ece222478b734e2c45","tid":716538,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"檢討自資專上教育專責小組公布諮詢文件，建議制定一套清晰的政策，規定發展情況和院校自身能力遜於原來計劃的營辦機構取消註冊。諮詢期至8月31日，小組計劃在今年底發表最終報告。<br />\n<br />\n小組又建議，保留高級文憑和副學士，但須將兩者的資歷重新定位，令兩者有明確區分。小組認為，副學士資歷可被定位為主要支援升讀一般學位課程，但仍可用作獨立資歷，以投身毋須專門技能的初階職位。小組又指，高級文憑資歷可被定位為主要支援升讀與職專教育相關的專門學位課程，同時亦可作為獨立資歷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/專責小組建議保留高級文憑和副學士-但資歷須重新定位-082520774.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%B0%88%E8%B2%AC%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99%E9%AB%98%E7%B4%9A%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E5%92%8C%E5%89%AF%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB-%E4%BD%86%E8%B3%87%E6%AD%B7%E9%A0%88%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D-082520774.html&d=j%2Fmkz3xy8RAYDM2hWATdMbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=7e09e559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/專責小組建議保留高級文憑和副學士-但資歷須重新定位-082520774.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪即管慢慢重新定位，反正讀嚟都晒q氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"2b837a3271b2d6d9f86bd1c3786efe75b692126d","tid":716538,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"副學士<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec51d43e5dacb65a2c3c96598c8bba916f68c1c2","tid":716538,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12